headline: ROLLINS, INC. INCREASES REGULAR QUARTERLY CASH DIVIDEND BY MORE THAN 10 PERCENT
summary: Rollins, Inc. (NYSE: ROL), a premier global consumer and commercial services company, announced that the Board of Directors declared a regular quarterly cash dividend on its common stock of $0.1825 per share payable December 10, 2025 to shareholders of record at the close of business on November 10, 2025. This represents an increase of approximately 11 percent from the same quarter a year ago.
